This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with analyzing and classifying cells and tissues using automated Computer Vision solutions. The use of Convolutional Neural Networks for this purpose also suggests that it may belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of Transfer Learning and End-to-End Learning techniques suggests that it may also belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the mention of a dataset of images suggests that it may also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
